title: Angel, Season 2
description:
Angel: the Series is a spin-off from Buffy the Vampire Slayer featuring the Slayers once romantic interest, the vampire with a soul. After he moves to LA in the first season, he soon cross blades with lawfirm Wolfram & Hart wich continues to be the series prime enemy even after the series came to and end.

This is the second season, a re-seed originating from Supernova.
